customSql.expressionStatement:
select 
`CustomerID`, `CompanyName`, `ContactName`, `ContactTitle`, `Address`,
  `City`, `Region`,  
  CONCAT(
    CASE WHEN (`Region` is NULL) THEN "UNKNOWN"  ELSE `Region` END,
    '-', 
    CASE WHEN (`PostalCode` is NULL) THEN "NO_PCODE"  ELSE `PostalCode` END
    )  as RegionCode,
  `PostalCode`, `Country`, `Phone`, `Fax`
  FROM ${customers}
